description: This file is a C header file that contains the prototype definitions for exported functions of the Content Filtering Authentication Message Management Object, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: CfAmmoComponentCreate
methods.description: Creates a new Content Filtering Authentication Message Management Object component.

methods.name: CfAmmoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Content Filtering Authentication Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfAmmoRemove
methods.description: Removes an instance of the Content Filtering Authentication Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfAmmoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the Content Filtering Authentication Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfAmmoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Content Filtering Authentication Message Management Object.
